  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK811">
<l>parukuvār pōliṉum paṇpilār kēṇmai </l>
<l>perukaliṟ kuṉṟa liṉitu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The decrease of friendship with those who look as if they would eat you up (through excess of love) while they are really destitute of goodness is far better than its increase.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
